snippet.title: Kajol Ne Banayi Prawns Biryani aur Dilip Bana DDLJ Ka Shah Rukh Khan! @FarahKhanK
snippet.description:
Hi guys! Aaj hamare ghar aa rahi hain Kajol! 🤩 Karenge bahot saari masti aur baatein, unki new movie ‘MAA’ par bhi discuss karenge. Saath hi banayenge yummy prawns biryani, aur Dilip banega DDLJ wala Shah Rukh Khan!

Jab mehmaan nawazi mein koi kasar baaki na ho, tab jaan lo ghar mein aaj Daawat hai 💛

This #WorldBiryaniDay, Farah & Dilip are cooking up a storm—delicious Prawn Biryani for none other than Kajol!
What’s the secret behind this perfect plate? Daawat Basmati Rice – long-grained, aromatic, and made for moments that matter.

Celebrate flavour, friendship, and everything biryani on 6th July with #DaawatWorldBiryaniDay

Don't forget to subscribe and hit the notification bell so you never miss out on my latest recipes and cooking adventures!

Click here to subscribe my channel:- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChCYMXLO_SfiNwOc2rlNKCA?sub_confirmation=1

Brand Enquiry: farah.khan@qyuki.com

Also follow me on:-
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/farahkhankunder/

snippet.title: Mangli Renuka Yellamma | Bonalu Song 2025 | Full Song | Suresh Bobbili | Indravathi | Nakka Srikanth
snippet.description:
🎶 MANGLI RENUKA YELLAMMA | BONALU SONG 2025 🎉
Celebrate the divine power of Renuka Yellamma with this energetic Bonalu 2025 anthem! Sung by the sensational Mangli and composed by the dynamic Suresh Bobbili, this song is a tribute to Telangana’s rich folk culture and the fierce goddess worshipped across the region.

Feel the spiritual energy rise as beats, devotion, and traditional Telangana folk vibes come alive in this electrifying song.


#mangli  #manglisongs #bonalusong2025  #manglibonalusongs #telanganabonalu #bonalunewsongs #nakkasrikanth #oggukatha #baindlakatha #renukayellammasongs


Director - Damu Reddy 
Singers : Mangli, Nakka Srikanth Yadav & Indravathi Chauhan 
Music : Suresh Bobbili
Cherographey :  Shekar Virus 
Source : Oggu Katha & Bindla  Katha 
Sekarana : Nakka Srikanth Yadav
DOP - Tirupathi 
Editing: Nikhil Goud 
DI :  Mayasabha Studios 
Colorist : Anvesh
Stylist : Rishi Choudary 
Camera Assnts : Paramesh & Pencil Balu 
Publicity Designs : Rana 
Execution - Shiva Chauhan 
Manager : Megharaj 
Producer - Balu Nayak 

Makeup & Hair Done by swathis_makeup_academy  
Costume Disigner by : beauty meets  Fashion by Jeevana

*Special Thanks*
Jenwada Venkanna, Kamli Patel (DOP) & Dev Rathod

snippet.title: Vj Siddhu On Fire! | OG Sambavam - Part 2 | ROFL with Harshath Khan & Adirchi Arun | Sam Vishal
snippet.description:
Sambavam Reloaded ! 🔥
In this mad part 2 episode of Samodu Vilayadu, your favourite OG trio — VJ Siddhu, Harshath Khan, and Adirchi Arun — enter the game zone, and things go from wild to wilder!

🎯 Hosted by the ever-charming Sam Vishal, this episode is packed with:
💥 Unpredictable challenges
🤣 Uncontrollable laughter
🎮 Full-on competitive chaos
🔥 OG bromance energy

Will Siddhu and team survive the madness or break the game rules with their signature style?

👉 Watch now and get ready to LOL with the most rowdy, risky, and riotous episode of Samodu Vilayadu yet!

Oppaari song ah..
Vechaachu Vaanga..

Ella oorum paathuko
Thambi konjam thallikko
Coolie Varaan solliko..!

🌟 Welcome to Episode 02 of the Puri Yatra Special! 🌟
Join Middle Class Madhu and his hilarious family as they dive into the grandeur of Jagannath Rath Yatra in Puri! 🚩

This episode brings laughter, emotion, and a colorful cultural celebration like never before! Watch how Madhu’s parents, friends, and our beloved 1A Master team up to pull the chariot of Lord Jagannath, blending tradition with full-on FilmyMoji style comedy! 😂💥

From crowded rooftops to catchy dialogues, this is a visual feast filled with middle-class nostalgia, unity, and devotion.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

हो अपना अखियां में काजरा लगाके,
रखनी जुड़ा में साड़ी अटकाके,,
आ हमार पावडर क्रीम लागे हो जाई डिम बाटे एकही जगहिया खाली,,
हो सईया बिन नथुनिया के डाली,,

त चोली चिल्लाता ये राजा हो जल्दी आ जा हो,
कमर से साड़ी सरक जाता सीरिया जा हो,,
त करी अईसन सिंगार के 
बिन भतार के,
मन नाही करे रही झार के बिन भतार के,,
त कहे बिंदिया बलम तू सतावल कर कम लाल भईल बा घुसा से ओठलाली हो सईया बिन,,,

चूड़ी के शोर सखि भावे ना केहू बजावे ना,
सुना संगीत बा जवानी के केहू गावे ना,,
अब त लागे की कटी ना सर्दी ये बेदर्दी,
इ जवानी खेसारी के नामे मन करे करदी,,
रहिते घरे बलम होईत गाना गरम 
ओ में कबो कबो होईत कऊवाली ,, हो सइया बिन,,

Isme bhabhi chahti hai ki nanad ki shaadi jaldi se jaldi ho jaye – chahe love marriage ho ya arranged.

snippet.title: Inside a Village with No Doors, No Locks & No Theft!  (SHOCKING 😲)
snippet.description:
This is one of the most unique villages in india! This is shani shingnapur village

Could you imagine living in a house without a door? I couldn't either, until I set foot in Shani Shingnapur! This legendary village in India is famous for its unique custom: homes are built without any doors, relying solely on the divine protection of Lord Shani. But my curious mind had questions: How do people live like this? What about security? And are the tales of zero theft truly real?

In this video, I take you with me as I explore every corner of Shani Shani Shingnapur. I spoke to residents, witnessed daily life, and dug into the local lore surrounding the "no theft" phenomenon. Get ready for a fascinating look into a community built on faith and trust. This was truly an eye-opening experience!

snippet.title: Bala Speech Parandhu Po, Vetrimaaran Speech Parandhu Po | Parandhu Po Audio Launch
snippet.description:
Bala Speech Parandhu Po, Vetrimaaran Speech Parandhu Po | Parandhu Po Audio Launch

Bala Speech Parandhu Po audio launch.
Vetrimaaran speech Parandhu Po movie trailer launch.
Bala Vetrimaaran speech in Parandhu Po movie trailer launch. 

Presenting Director Bala, Director Vetrimaaran speech Parandhu Po movie. Parandhu Po movie audio and trailer launch happened in chennai today.

Paranthu Po is an 2025 Indian Tamil-language road musical comedy film written, directed and co-produced by Ram under his banner Seven Seas and Seven Hills Productions along with Disney+ Hotstar. The film stars Shiva and Mithul Ryan in the lead roles alongside Grace Antony, Anjali, Vijay Yesudas, Aju Varghese and others in important roles. The music and background score was composed by Santhosh Dhayanidhi and Yuvan Shankar Raja, while the cinematography and editing were handled by N. K. Ekambaram and Mathi V. S. respectively.

Parandhu Po is scheduled to release in theatres on 4 July 2025.

snippet.title: PASTA | Prawn Masala Pasta Recipe Cooking in Village | Spirali Pasta Recipe | Seafood Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cooked a spirali pasta recipe using fresh prawns and colorful, healthy vegetables. We first half-cooked the pasta, then added it to a hot, big pan along with the prawns. We also added hand-ground masala for traditional taste and healthy, colorful vegetables to make this pasta both nutritious and tasty.

Finally, we enjoyed the dish in the evening at our farm. The taste was spicy and delicious!

pl.title: MAKARON | Przepis na makaron z krewetkami i masalą Gotowanie w wiosce | Przepis na makaron Spiral...
pl.description:
Dzisiaj w naszej wiosce ugotowaliśmy przepis na makaron spirali ze świeżymi krewetkami i kolorowymi, zdrowymi warzywami. Najpierw ugotowaliśmy makaron w połowie, a następnie dodaliśmy go do gorącej, dużej patelni razem z krewetkami. Dodaliśmy również mieloną ręcznie masalę dla tradycyjnego smaku i zdrowe, kolorowe warzywa, aby ten makaron był zarówno pożywny, jak i smaczny.

Na koniec, wieczorem delektowaliśmy się daniem na naszej farmie. Smak był pikantny i pyszny!

fr-FR.title: PÂTES | Recette de pâtes aux crevettes masala | Recette de pâtes spirales | Recette de fruits de mer
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons cuisiné des pâtes spirali avec des crevettes fraîches et des légumes sains et colorés. Nous avons d'abord mi-cuit les pâtes, puis les avons placées dans une grande poêle chaude avec les crevettes. Nous avons également ajouté du masala moulu à la main pour un goût traditionnel et des légumes sains et colorés pour des pâtes à la fois nutritives et savoureuses.

Nous avons finalement dégusté ce plat le soir à la ferme. C'était épicé et délicieux !

hi.title: पास्ता | झींगा मसाला पास्ता रेसिपी गांव में खाना बनाना | स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी | समुद्री भोजन रे...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताज़े झींगे और रंग-बिरंगी, सेहतमंद सब्ज़ियों का इस्तेमाल करके स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी बनाई। हमने पहले पास्ता को आधा पकाया, फिर उसे झींगों के साथ एक गर्म, बड़े पैन में डाला। हमने पारंपरिक स्वाद के लिए हाथ से पिसा हुआ मसाला और सेहतमंद, रंग-बिरंगी सब्ज़ियाँ भी डालीं, ताकि यह पास्ता पौष्टिक और स्वादिष्ट दोनों बन सके।

आखिरकार, हमने शाम को अपने खेत में इस डिश का लुत्फ़ उठाया। इसका स्वाद मसालेदार और लज़ीज़ था!

ja.title: パスタ | エビマサラパスタのレシピ 村で調理 | スパイラリパスタのレシピ | シーフードのレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なエビと色とりどりのヘルシー野菜を使ったスパイラルパスタを作りました。パスタを半分ほど茹でてから、熱した大きなフライパンにエビと一緒に入れました。伝統的な味にするために、手挽きのマサラとヘルシーで色とりどりの野菜を加え、栄養価が高く、おいしいパスタに仕上げました。

最後に、農場で夕食を楽しみました。スパイシーでとても美味しかったです！

de-DE.title: PASTA | Rezept für Garnelen-Masala-Pasta im Dorf kochen | Spiral-Pasta-Rezept | Meeresfrüchte-Rezept
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein Rezept für Spiralnudeln mit frischen Garnelen und buntem, gesundem Gemüse gekocht. Wir haben die Nudeln zunächst halb gekocht und dann zusammen mit den Garnelen in eine große, heiße Pfanne gegeben. Für den traditionellen Geschmack haben wir handgemahlenes Masala und gesundes, buntes Gemüse hinzugefügt, um die Nudeln nahrhaft und lecker zu machen.

Abends haben wir das Gericht auf unserem Bauernhof genossen. Es schmeckte würzig und köstlich!

nl-NL.title: PASTA | Garnalen Masala Pasta Recept Koken in Dorp | Spirali Pasta Recept | Zeevruchten Recept
nl-NL.description:
Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een recept voor spirali pasta met verse garnalen en kleurrijke, gezonde groenten. We kookten de pasta eerst half gaar en deden die vervolgens in een hete, grote pan, samen met de garnalen. We voegden er handgemalen masala aan toe voor de traditionele smaak en gezonde, kleurrijke groenten om de pasta zowel voedzaam als lekker te maken.

Tot slot hebben we 's avonds op onze boerderij van het gerecht genoten. Het was pittig en heerlijk!

ko.title: 파스타 | 마을에서 요리하는 새우 마살라 파스타 레시피 | 스파이럴리 파스타 레시피 | 해산물 레시피
ko.description:
오늘 저희 마을에서는 신선한 새우와 알록달록하고 건강에 좋은 채소를 넣어 스파이럴 파스타 레시피를 만들어 봤습니다. 파스타를 반쯤 익힌 후, 뜨겁고 큰 팬에 새우와 함께 넣었습니다. 전통적인 맛을 위해 손으로 간 마살라를, 영양가 있고 맛있는 채소를 더하기 위해 건강하고 알록달록한 채소를 넣었습니다.

마지막으로 저녁 농장에서 맛있게 먹었습니다. 매콤하면서도 정말 맛있었어요!

pt-BR.title: MASSAS | Receita de Massa Masala com Camarão | Cozinhando na Vila | Receita de Massa em Espiral |...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos uma receita de macarrão espiral com camarões frescos e vegetais coloridos e saudáveis. Primeiro, cozinhamos o macarrão pela metade e depois o colocamos em uma panela grande e quente junto com os camarões. Também adicionamos masala moído à mão para um sabor tradicional e vegetais saudáveis ​​e coloridos para tornar este macarrão nutritivo e saboroso.

Por fim, apreciamos o prato à noite em nossa fazenda. O sabor era picante e delicioso!

it.title: PASTA | Ricetta della pasta con gamberi e masala | Cucinare nel villaggio | Ricetta della pasta a...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato una pasta a spirale con gamberi freschi e verdure colorate e salutari. Abbiamo prima cotto la pasta a metà cottura, poi l'abbiamo messa in una padella grande e calda insieme ai gamberi. Abbiamo anche aggiunto masala macinato a mano per un sapore tradizionale e verdure sane e colorate per rendere questa pasta nutriente e gustosa.

Infine, abbiamo gustato il piatto la sera nella nostra fattoria. Il sapore era piccante e delizioso!

id.title: PASTA | Resep Pasta Masala Udang Masak di Desa | Resep Pasta Spirali | Resep Makanan Laut
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak resep pasta spirali menggunakan udang segar dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan. Pertama-tama kami memasak pasta setengah matang, lalu memasukkannya ke dalam wajan besar yang panas bersama udang. Kami juga menambahkan masala yang digiling dengan tangan untuk cita rasa tradisional dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan agar pasta ini bergizi dan lezat.

Akhirnya, kami menikmati hidangan ini di malam hari di pertanian kami. Rasanya pedas dan lezat!

es-US.title: PASTA | Receta de pasta masala con langostinos | Receta de pasta espiral | Receta de mariscos
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, cocinamos una receta de pasta espiral con gambas frescas y verduras coloridas y saludables. Primero, cocinamos la pasta a medias y luego la pusimos en una sartén grande y caliente junto con las gambas. También añadimos masala molida a mano para darle un sabor tradicional y verduras coloridas y saludables, lo que hizo que esta pasta fuera nutritiva y sabrosa.

Por último, disfrutamos del plato por la noche en nuestra granja. ¡El sabor era picante y delicioso!

snippet.description:

https://www.amazon.in/shop/masalakitchenaam  

👉My Shoot Equipment: https://www.amazon.in/shop/masalakitchen/list/2QKZIYG6AOAV7?ref_=aipsflist 
----------------------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐓𝐄𝐃 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒:
Mix Achar
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ev_K5eWMULA 

Mix Veg Achar
https://youtu.be/H4srsxfcRIA?si=uC6ry8ih7MMmXzTA 

Mirch, Adrak, Lehsun Ka Achar
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lTCrzjVqcQ 

Hari Mirchi Ka Achar
https://youtu.be/Wb5Od-drZ9c?si=PP-_n_WmtX3wWZfw 

Red Chili Pickle
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-sV88oHFu0 
--------------------------------------------------
✍🏻𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐒: 
Raw Mango (कैरी) - 3 Kg
Salt (नमक) - 6 Tbsp 
Turmeric Powder (हल्दी पाउडर) - 1-1.5 Tbsp
Coriander Seeds (सूखा साबुत धनिया) - 1/4 Cup
Dry Red Chili (सूखी लाल मिर्च) - 10 Nos. 
Thick Fennel Seeds (मोटी सौंफ) - 1/4 Cup
Fenugreek Seeds (मेथी दाना) - 2 Tsp
Cumin Seeds (जीरा) - 2 Tsp
Yellow Mustard Seeds (पिली राई दाल) - 1/4 Cup
Nigella Seeds/Black Onion Seeds (कलौंजी) - 1 Tsp
Kashmiri Red Chili Powder (कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर) - 3-4 Tbsp
Thick Fennel Seeds (मोटी सौंफ) - 1/8 Cup
Asafetida (हींग) - 1 Tsp
Black Salt (काला नमक) - As Per Taste
Mustard Oil (सरसों का तेल) - 1 Cup
Jaggery (गुड़) - 1 Tbsp
Salt (नमक) - 1 Tbsp
---------------------------------------------------
Aaj Hum Bana Rahe Hain Ek Bilkul Desi Style Mein Aam Ka Achar, Jo Na Sirf Chatpata Hai Balki Mahino Tak Chalne Wala Hai. Agar Aap Dhoond Rahe Hain Aam Ka Achar Kaise Banate Hain Ya How To Make Mango Pickle, Toh Yeh Video Aapke Liye Perfect Hai.

Isme Aapko Milegi Ek Authentic Traditional Aam Ka Achar Recipe, Jo Inspired Hai Aam Ka Achar Bihari Style Se. Humne Use Kiya Hai Fresh Kairi Ka Achar Banane Ka Desi Tarika – Bilkul Masala Kitchen Style Mein! Yeh Hai Ek Spicy Raw Mango Pickle Recipe, Jise Aap Bina Kisi Preservative Ke Long Time Store Kar Sakte Hain.

Toh Chaliye Dekhte Hain Aam Ka Achar Banane Ki Vidhi, Step-By-Step, Jo Hai Asaan Aur Super Tasty – Jaise Mango Pickle Recipe By Poonam Aur Ghar Ka Banaya Hua Aam Ka Achaar!

snippet.title: Adhure Supne | New Punjabi Series 2025 | JaggieTV
snippet.description:
Adhure Supne (Incomplete Dreams) A powerful story of struggle, dreams, and resilience.
In a world where every character is battling their own demons, Jaggi stands out — a young man with immense musical talent but no money to chase his dream. While he’s determined to record his songs and make his mark, his family pushes him to abandon his passion and take up a "real job."
Torn between expectations and ambition, Jaggi keeps sacrificing his dreams... until Seerat enters his life. Together, they face life's toughest challenges, stand tall against society, and fight to keep their dreams alive.
Will their incomplete dreams ever be fulfilled?Can passion survive in a world full of pressure?
Watch now to witness this emotional journey filled with inspiration, love, and the fire to never give up! 🔥

Producer: Jaggie Rajgarh
Executive Manager: Simardeep Singh
Production Manager: Dharminder Singh
